utility. This required evidentiary demonstration concerns the reasonable compensation for stranded costs. We
request comments on what is reasonable compensation: 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
