<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
 The U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service (Service) gives notice that the deadline to determine whether the northern copperbelly
water snake (
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=3 -->
Nerodia erythrogaster neglecta
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
